deleteAllDensityAreas(25.10)                      deleteAllDensityAreas(25.10)

Name
       deleteAllDensityAreas  -  Removes  all partial placement blockages from
       the floorplan

Syntax
       deleteAllDensityAreas

       [-help]

       Removes all partial placement blockages from the  floorplan.  Use  this
       command after importing the design.

Parameters
       -help  Outputs  a  brief  description of the deleteAllDensityAreas com-
              mand.

              For a detailed description of the command, use the man command:

              man deleteAllDensityAreas

Related Information
              * createDensityArea

              * setSelectedDensityArea

              * Floorplanning the Design chapter in the Innovus User Guide

